Flip4Mac WMV Components allow you to import, export and play Windows Media video and audio files on your Mac. Flip4Mac WMV export components can be used with QuickTime Pro, Final Cut Pro, Compressor, and iMovie (iMovie '08 and '09 not supported).

MWV Player Pro

* Import WMV files for editing and conversion to QuickTime formats

* Move Windows Media files into your iPod

* Edit your movies from your digital camera

Systgem Requirements

Mac OS X (on Intel or PowerPC) Version 10.4 and higher
